OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRelax rules on illegal drug
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fresearch, say advisers     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Independent government advisers have   
OL,6, called for rule changes to allow more  
OL,7, research into therapeutic uses of      
OL,8, illegal drugs, including psychedelics. 
OL,10,FThe Advisory Council on the Misuse of  
OL,11,FDrugs (ACMD) proposes easing controls  
OL,12,Fon trials using Schedule 1 drugs -     
OL,13,Fwhich include opium and LSD.           
OL,15,FRecent studies have found psychedelics 
OL,16,Fcould help treat severe depression.    
OL,18,FMP Charlotte Nichols said further      
OL,19,Fresearch could lead to "transformative 
OL,20,Fmental health treatments".             
